controls.description:
Mechanisms exist to identify components that potentially impact the organization's ability to execute contingency plans, including changes to:
(1) Personnel roles;
(2) Business processes (including the use of third-party services);
(3) Deployed technologies; 
(4) Data repositories and/or data flows; and/or
(5) Physical infrastructure.

